OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fwarm evening to end Monday, though any
OL,7,Flate sunshine may be rather hazy. Low
OL,8,Fcloud and fog spreading inland from
OL,9,Fthe west overnight, bringing mist and
OL,10,Fmurk by dawn plus spots of drizzle. A
OL,11,Fmild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FLow cloud clearing during the
OL,14,Fmorning. A very warm day follows with
OL,15,Fplenty of strong sunshine, though
OL,16,Fcloud may push into the far north.
OL,17,FLight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
